" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/xingke-think" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$xingke-think'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/d66ce6c410c26c9c9a5c1b51ba522cce_l.jpg" alt="邢可" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/pan-duo-la-99-73" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$pan-duo-la-99-73'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-191b1b62dacdd2fabc87fb07ffcda813_l.jpg" alt="潘工" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/SODOyuwen" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$SODOyuwen'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6618b3b4cd8c137c8f2e59f72641b096_l.jpg" alt="宇文妍" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/xiao-yu-92-72" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-yu-92-72'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a559d30e3cf5e92c42ee2140c0d8cd36_l.jpg" alt="晓渔" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/maxwell_sun" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$maxwell_sun'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/56f24c1d414419d5e9b574035a21f6fb_l.jpg" alt="Maxwell Sun" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/kou-50-59" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$kou-50-59'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ecbd95fb891a8c1c51c47973043ebab2_l.jpg" alt="库兹马" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/the-one-14" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$the-one-14'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bb7eee3ca158767a2f760133595e3f71_l.jpg" alt="Edison" class="avatar d50"></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="module"><div class="module-header"><h3><a href="/roundtable">查看全部圆桌活动 »</a></h3></div></div><div class="module"><div class="global-footer"><ul><li><a href="https://liukanshan.zhihu.com" target="_blank">刘看山</a></li><li><a href="javascript:;" id="js-feedback-button">建议反馈</a></li><li><a href="/app" target="_blank">移动应用</a></li><li><a href="/careers">招聘</a></li><li><a href="/question/19581624" target="_blank">知乎指南</a></li><li><a href="/terms" target